cohortName: Human immunodeficiency virus infection referent incident cohort
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (439727) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: Human immunodeficiency virus infection referent prevalent cohort
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (439727) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history, with at least 365 days of prior continuous observation. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: HIV excluding HIV-II design diagnostics 1 cohort
logicDescription: Excludes HIV II, and HIV negative. Has finding of HIV status which may indicate positive
